'''Vyaz''' ({{lang-ru|'''вязь'''}} from  {{lang-ru|'''вязать'''}}, {{lang|ru-Latn|vyazat}}; ({{lang-ua|'''в'язь'''}} from  {{lang-ua|'''в'язати'''}} 
{{lang-cu|'''вѩзати'''}}, {{lang|cu-Latn|vięzati}} 'to bind, to tie') is a type of [[Cyrillic]] ornate lettering.

